org.rapla.entities.dynamictype

Interface DynamicType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Annotatable, Cloneable, Entity<DynamicType>, EntityPermissionContainer<DynamicType>, LastChangedTimestamp, MultiLanguageNamed, Named, Ownable, PermissionContainer, RaplaObject<DynamicType>, Timestamp

    public interface DynamicType
extends EntityPermissionContainer<DynamicType>, MultiLanguageNamed, Annotatable, Timestamp
    In rapla it is possible to dynamicly classify a reservation, resource or person with customized attributes. You can for example define a dynamicType called room with the attributes name and seats and classify all your room-resources as room.
